Data Analytics on Cosmetics Sales using Excel
This project demonstrates data analytics on a cosmetics sales dataset using Microsoft Excel.
Imported and cleaned raw sales data.
Applied Pivot Tables to summarize and analyze key metrics (sales by product, region, category, etc.).
Designed interactive dashboards for better visualization of trends and insights.
Created multiple data visualizations (charts & graphs) to highlight sales performance.
The project is intended as a practical example of Excel-based business data analysis and can be extended to other retail/consumer datasets.
